        <p><span class="SetOffFirstLevel"><MadCap:keyword term="Source Control Explorer:Pending Changes pane" />Source Control Explorer </span>With the Pending Changes pane open, select the files or folders that you want to revert, right-click, and select <span class="Emphasis">Source Control &gt; Revert</span>. You can also click <span class="Emphasis">Revert</span> to revert all files in the <MadCap:keyword term="Source control:include changes" />Included Changes section.</p>
